::Child answered gigatron:::

Child: 'If the Maximals do not except then the matrix will give us strength 
to create. Now i need you all to begin working. Mother would you and Data 
collect your angel papers. Father you and defection collect your alchemy 
work. Gigatron prep the ships. Skyschorchers collect some weaponry and load 
it in one of the ships, we have to be prepared! Now that you all have 
instructions i will meditate."

:::Child sat down on the spot and meditated. his mind began to fill with 
visions of Vulois. He saw him as... as.... as an Alliance Member! But it 
couldn't be. Child dismissed the dream and went on to others....:::
